{"tid":1063754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"存在就是痛苦","createTime":"2019-03-16T04:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T08:03:10.000Z","uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb3752e0e76fa4b0c378da99dd52b3f38938d2b","tid":1063754,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"一個人好命<br />\n未行過仆街運<br />\n可能冇乜感覺<br />\n<br />\n但對小弟𠵱啲<br />\n一出世就行梗仆街運嚟講<br />\n存在就係一種痛苦<br />\n<br />\n一個人最痛苦<br />\n未必係受過幾多苦難<br />\n而係當你喺仆街運當中<br />\n好努力咁求變<br />\n結果都係事倍功半<br />\n甚至徒勞無功<br />\n換嚟只有責怪同不屑<br />\n人生好似只得無奈<br />\n<br />\n可以埋怨嘅好多<br />\n出生唔好<br />\n命同際遇差<br />\n事業、愛情、經濟皆失意<br />\n<br />\n但如果本身冇存在過<br />\n根本冇嘢需要埋怨<br />\n亦冇嘢需要責怪<br />\n所以存在就係痛苦嘅來源<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d4cdc3c5ae69a2c8d2df7b11891d4d79207fa4","tid":1063754,"uid":232456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"是的<br />\n如果可以揀，我希望自己從未存在過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652826a3e387495b51db8c5c4fcf1438f0b528cd","tid":1063754,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d4cdc3c5ae69a2c8d2df7b11891d4d79207fa4","tid":1063754,"uid":232456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"是的<br />\n如果可以揀，我希望自己從未存在過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d1b4254c5124409e9e78fc7d0c968fb7b8a752","tid":1063754,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"